HEADWORD: Stram
<hw>Stram</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <ety>[Cf. LG.
<ets>strammen</ets> to strain, straiten, stretch, D. <ets>stram</ets>
strained, tight, G. <ets>stramm</ets>.]</ety> <def>To spring or recoil
with violence.</def> <mark>[Prov. Eng.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Stram</ent>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Stram
<hw>Stram</hw>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <def>To dash down; to beat.</def>
<mark>[Prov. Eng.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

